`/AGENTS.md` is the canonical workspace operating contract. Follow its instruction precedence, autonomy limits, phased project lifecycle, file-role boundaries, validation standard, and completion standard.

Do not leave durable rules only in chat. Do not defer agent-capable work to the user. Do not store secret values in agent files. Preserve current state and unresolved evidence before context loss.
